{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The washing facilities was one room, with around the wall was a trough, like a pig trough where they feed the pigs in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And above that, about a foot or so above it, there was a pipe-- a water pipe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Little holes were drilled in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was where the water came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, in the wintertime, that would splash all over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as high as the trough was, you would have the whole room one sheet of ice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So to-- to get the energy to wash yourselves was-- was something what took a lot of-- a lot of willpower because everybody was hungry.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody was feeling lousy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So everybody was dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to keep yourselves clean was a big-- a big undertaking, especially in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you didn't, you would even more would be more susceptible to the sicknesses of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what we did, we would take a rock and put steps into the ice to get into the washroom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was Posen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, they gave up on the building that lake because the war machine was getting too close.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they they sending the Polish worker into Germany to work for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, we would be digging ditches for the sewer-- city sewer lines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And being a plumber, I was lucky, later on, to be able to work on laying the-- the sewer lines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working with Polish workers then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there, again, I was able to get some extra food shoved to the side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people started liking me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They saw I was-- I didn't know-- I was working with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
